---- Step 1:
$ cd src
$ qtcreator &

---- Step 2: generate Makefile etc in a shadow build config:
In Qt Creator:
- click on 'Open Project'
- open CMakeLists.txt
- select another directory than src/ as the build location (the default, ../src-build, is fine)
- click on 'Run CMake'
- click on 'Finish'

---- Step 3: edit source files:
- open src/first.cpp, modify, and save

---- Step 4 (option 1): compile from Qt Creator
- Control+B

---- Step 4 (option 2): compile from terminal:
$ cd ../src-build
$ make

---- Step 5 (option 1): run from Qt Creator:
- Control+R (which will also compile first if necessary)

--- Step 5 (option 2): run from terminal:
$ cd ../src-build
$ ./program_options
